fields.name: MOCK EXAMPLE Clinical-Only Data License
fields.internal_description:
Use of this data and associated metadata is subject to the MOCK EXAMPLE Clinical-Only Data License.

This data is private and confidential, and is intended ONLY to be used for clinical diagnostic purposes by authorized persons. It must not be shared publicly, or with those not authorized to access it. Use of the data and/or metadata restricted to the purposes detailed by a donor consent policy.

Serious criminal and/or civil penalties my apply for misuse or unintended disclosure of this data and/or metadata.

fields.name: MOCK EXAMPLE Research Data License
fields.internal_description:
Use of this data and associated metadata is subject to the MOCK EXAMPLE Research Data License.

This data and/or metadata is NOT associated with a human subject and is NOT subject to a donor consent policy. It can be shared with the consent of the data owner(s).

This data and metadata may be covered by an additional appropriate licence (eg CC-BY).
